warehouse.simulator.model

Class Motor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • warehouse.simulator.model.Motor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, IMotor

    public class Motor
extends java.lang.Thread
implements IMotor
    Motor class of the simulation. Responsible for excecuting all events that happen in the simulation. The motor handles communication with all of the other model layer classes and communicates to SimulationController.
    Author:
    Jere Salmensaari
